text: Ali Germaine Landry (born July 21, 1973) is an American actress and former Miss USA. She is also a model. She was the Doritos girl in television commercials. She won the Miss USA pageant in 1996. Landry was born in Breaux Bridge, Louisiana. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Actors from Louisiana Category:American models Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Beauty pageant winners Category:Miss USA
